Core solutions and management tools

    Core solutions
        - IOT solutions
            - IOT Hub - eg thermostat sending messages to hub 
            - IOT Central
            - Azure sphere - a platform designed to work with connected devices
                    - includes - a secure silicon chip
                               - Sphere OS
                               - Cloud based security services
                               
        - Big data and Analystics solutions
            - Azure Synapse - formerly known as SQL data warehouse
            - HD Insight - umbrella term used to refer to hadoop, spark and other big data technologies
            - Azure Databricks - IDE on cloud
            
         - AI solutions
            - Azure machine learning
            - cognitive services
            - azure bot services
                  - natural language chabot service
                  - database of FAQs
                  - front end that allows people to ask questions and get answers
                  
          - Serverless solutions
             - Azure functions
             - azure logic apps - workflow based - eg : when http request is recd, test function, create blob
             - event grid
             
          
          - azure devops solutions
             - azure devops
             - github
             - github actions
                    - automate software workflows
                    - what happens once someone checks in changes to the code?
                    - possibly includes continius integrations
                    - possibly includes automation compilation of code to check for errors
                    - possibly includes running a suite of tests againt the code
             - azure devtest labs
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
             
